</a>
<a href="mailto:?subject=Convocation 2019: 'Youâ¬"ll always be our best ambassadors'&body=1,000-plus fall graduates are inspired to take pride in their accomplishments%0D%0A%0D%0Ahttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.concordia.ca%2Fcunews%2Fmain%2Fstories%2F2019%2F11%2F19%2Fconvocation-2019-you-ll-always-be-our-best-ambassadors.html%3Futm_source%3Demail%26utm_medium%3Dshare">
